                            <p class="mb-6 text-lg">
                                Exploring the concept of "vibe coding" and how the atmosphere and energy of development environments impact productivity and
                                creativity.
                            </p>
                            <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4">
                                <a href="https://www.communitypulse.io/97-vibe-coding" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="btn btn-lg"
                                    >Listen Now</a
                                >
