                            <p class="mb-6 text-lg">
                                Discussing the establishment and importance of the DevRel Foundation in supporting and advancing the developer relations
                                community.
                            </p>
                            <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4">
                                <a
                                    href="https://www.communitypulse.io/93-the-devrel-foundation"
                                    target="_blank"
